        <item>
            <title>2.10.2</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 21:24:46 +0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>22</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.10.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>11.5</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul><li>Snippets that contain both inline images and {{field}} prompts now paste fully — the image is no longer dropped when you fill in a field</li><li>Restored the Insert menu in the snippet editor to add dynamic placeholders ({time}, {uuid}, {clipboard}, dates) and {{field}} prompts at the cursor</li><li>New "What you can add" info popover next to Content explains text, images, files, and dynamic tokens at a glance</li><li>Minor layout polish in the snippet editor</li></ul>]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/jaynguyen-vn/gen-snippets/releases/download/v2.10.2/GenSnippets.2.10.2.dmg" length="2740225" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="lWxifVo/nxzBzByEh9TOvbbhL/ONCKpCZdlWPwlN15+sgFC/zecpYXv6+GeEwHcXVNdq5G/4l4AjbvzkXipnDg=="/>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.10.1</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 20:13:00 +0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>21</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.10.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>11.5</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul><li>Snippet content now follows the system theme — text is readable in dark mode instead of staying dark</li><li>Inline images show at a tidy preview size in the editor (full resolution is kept for pasting)</li><li>The content editor auto-grows with your text and has a drag handle to resize it; double-click the handle to auto-fit</li><li>Description field uses the normal system font; cleaner contrast and borders throughout the dark theme</li></ul>]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/jaynguyen-vn/gen-snippets/releases/download/v2.10.1/GenSnippets.2.10.1.dmg" length="2697044" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="5QG5nkvV5HycFfd8LEwZBdVzVK1sS4Um/031AdV8Helm64+4w6/yfnMacg5S5iM98V8ZXQHh4s5uN1yZbglFCQ=="/>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.10.0</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 12:19:09 +0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>20</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.10.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>11.5</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul><li>Snippets can now mix text and inline images in a single rich-text document — trigger once to paste a whole formatted block</li><li>New Add Image / Add File toolbar in the snippet editor; paste or drop images right into the text</li><li>Smart paste per app: rich-text apps (Notes, TextEdit, Mail) get text + inline images in one paste; chat apps (Slack, Discord) receive the text and images correctly too</li><li>Dynamic placeholders ({time}, {uuid}, {clipboard}, dates) work inside rich snippets</li><li>Plain-text snippets are unchanged — {cursor} and {{field}} prompts keep working</li></ul>]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/jaynguyen-vn/gen-snippets/releases/download/v2.10.0/GenSnippets.2.10.0.dmg" length="2685173" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="vdrSnGQJtNYkdhl3CNrYfbwT+hg92fg4IU1Xoj8Rd7aYvXhp/S4JkN+AKlt1X8N9QWZE9FPKF0wGr0B3VtA0Cg=="/>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.9.17</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 10:10:00 +0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>19</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.9.17</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>11.5</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul><li>Fixed snippet expansion in cmux terminal — the typed command no longer stays on screen with stray characters before the replacement</li><li>cmux now uses the same reliable timing as iTerm2, Terminal.app and Warp for long-lived terminal sessions</li></ul>]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/jaynguyen-vn/gen-snippets/releases/download/v2.9.17/GenSnippets.2.9.17.dmg" length="2490503" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="VmitSIXEG+3qkKSvCOpfPfr55t481ZltwD6irb1BiKX3hwVzovtzttCeeTyMIfwudeUjUaVyY8fjkitnQr/kBg=="/>
