        <item>
            <title>2.9.15</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 23:25:00 +0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>17</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.9.15</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>11.5</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul><li>Fix snippets like <code>;ggp</code> intermittently failing to expand when typed in rapid succession</li><li>Decouple expansion lock from clipboard restore — release ~30ms after paste instead of 300ms so consecutive expansions no longer drop user keystrokes</li><li>Tighten duplicate-character dedup window from 100ms → 30ms to allow fast typing of repeated characters (e.g. the double <code>g</code> in <code>;ggp</code>)</li></ul>]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/jaynguyen-vn/gen-snippets/releases/download/v2.9.15/GenSnippets.2.9.15.dmg" length="2490548" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="//bccdhtaq7EOXsnizKakuB/zNDIntSQcHqwXmXX3Rr2uGy5KmS1/Pc95IqLXvC8IK7AMF8wDVxntKVU3dSeBw=="/>
